Download The Dataset

Click on the red button  located at the top of step name to download the datasets


Get Data From File


1.    Open Power BI Desktop

2.    In the Nav pane, click Get data

3.    Browse for the file downloaded in the previous step

4.    In the navigator window, select "STD Cases"

5. Click "Load"
